      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know about the syndrome thing but he's really miserable right now and i don't have any tylenol at home. i've used aspirin for my own headaches for years and it's always worked fine. isn't it just a standard painkiller? i'm sure a little bit won't hurt if his fever gets higher.",
